     The science fiction element is much stronger in his unfinished sequel. Which was said he could not finish the novel due to his inability to deal and write about the Nazi mentality.<br>
     Does evil exist? Is the road to Hell really paved with good intentions, that evil exists in everyone, good and bad, and it takes distressingly little to bring it to the surface. <br>
     I will not say it isn't a good book, just I don't like the storyline.<br>
     But we have to remember this is science fiction, for the U.S.A. is standing tall and proud and that is reality.<br>
